OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FRates of type 2 diabetes are rising
OL,8,Ftwice as fast in younger women than
OL,9,Fcompared to older women, according to
OL,10,Fnew analysis.
OL,12,FThe figure could be down to "little or
OL,13,Fno follow-up care" for those who
OL,14,Fdevelop the condition while pregnant,
OL,15,Faccording to the charity Diabetes UK.
OL,17,FGestational diabetes (GD) happens when
OL,18,Fwomen cannot produce enough insulin
OL,19,Fwhile pregnant, leading to high blood
OL,20,Fsugar.
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
