OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779987954
OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FThe first annual gestational diabetes
OL,8,Faudit, which was published last year
OL,9,Fby NHS England, showed that only 57%
OL,10,Fof women had an annual HbA1c test
OL,11,Fafter having GD.
OL,13,FIt also showed that more than one in
OL,14,F10 (11%) of women with GD developed
OL,15,Fprediabetes within a year, while 15%
OL,16,Fdeveloped type 2 diabetes within 10
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,F"These figures should be a wake-up
OL,20,Fcall," said Colette Marshall, chief
OL,21,Fexecutive at Diabetes UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779987954
OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,F"Type 2 diabetes is rising twice as
OL,8,Ffast in younger women compared to
OL,9,Folder women, and a crucial opportunity
OL,10,Ffor prevention is being missed.
OL,12,F"Every diagnosis is life-changing, but
OL,13,Fwhen it develops in younger people,
OL,14,Ftype 2 diabetes is even more
OL,15,Faggressive.
OL,17,F"Pregnancy shouldn't be a pathway to
OL,18,Fill health. Yet despite facing a much
OL,19,Fhigher risk of type 2 diabetes, too
OL,20,Fmany women with GD receive little or
OL,21,Fno follow-up care after pregnancy."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
