PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779987954
OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FMeg, 33, a teacher from Somerset, was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with gestational diabetes in
OL,9,F2020 when pregnant with her son.
OL,11,FSix years later, she has still not had
OL,12,Fa postnatal check-up regarding
OL,13,Fdiabetes risks.
OL,15,F"I had gestational diabetes for the
OL,16,Flast two weeks of my pregnancy, before
OL,17,Fmy son arrived prematurely at 29
OL,18,Fweeks," Meg said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
