FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779987954
OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,F"I was given no information about my
OL,8,Fincreased risk of developing type 2
OL,9,Fdiabetes and the steps I could take to
OL,10,Fprevent it.
OL,12,F"I had a phone call with my GP after
OL,13,Fthe birth, but there weren't any
OL,14,Fdiscussions about my gestational
OL,15,Fdiabetes.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
