OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779987954
OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,F"I'm surprised that I never had follow-
OL,8,Fup HbA1c checks, particularly as I'm
OL,9,Fconsidered high risk for type 2
OL,10,Fdiabetes, not only because of the
OL,11,Fgestational diabetes, but also because
OL,12,FI have polyendocrine metabolic ovarian
OL,13,Fsyndrome and family members with type
OL,14,F2 diabetes.
OL,16,F"Having clear facts about what
OL,17,Fgestational diabetes means for you
OL,18,Fduring and after pregnancy, and how to
OL,19,Fmanage it, would have made me feel so
OL,20,Fmuch more supported, both physically
OL,21,Fand mentally."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU}D@NO]
