OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FDiabetes UK has written to women's
OL,8,Fhealth minister Baroness Merron,
OL,9,Fcalling for urgent action to bolster
OL,10,Fpostnatal support for those with GD.
OL,12,FAround 4.7 million people in the UK
OL,13,Fare living with a diabetes diagnosis,
OL,14,Falthough Diabetes UK estimates almost
OL,15,F1.3 million have undiagnosed type 2
OL,16,Fdiabetes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
