OL,3,CPostnatal failings blamed for rising
OL,4,Crates of type 2 diabetes in younger
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FType 2, which impacts 90% of people
OL,8,Fliving with diabetes, happens when the
OL,9,Fbody is unable to make enough insulin
OL,10,For the insulin created doesn't work
OL,11,Fproperly.
OL,13,FSymptoms for type 2 diabetes can also
OL,14,Fbe easier to miss because they appear
OL,15,Fmuch slower than they do for type 1,
OL,16,Fand may go unnoticed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
